item.title: IC Women’s SICK-O performance
item.author: Andrada Balmez,Xinjin Ho,
item.description: To kick off the 2016⁄17 season, the women of disc Doctors (dD) took part in the annual SICKO Indoors Ultimate Frisbee tournament held in Brighton from the 8th to the 9th of October 2016. Things weren’t looking great for us at the start. It was the first week back at University and it dawned on …
